Turn flow:

1. Engine switches turn counter and finds next Character.
2. Engine retrieves Behaviour for Character.
3. Engine retrieves current Piggy value.
4. For each Ability.targets in Character.abilities:
    a. Engine simulates Ability+Target combination (see #6).
    b. Engine retrieves Piggy value.
    c. Engine ties Piggy value to Ability reference.
5. Engine deems Ability with highest Piggy to be used.
6. Engine performs Ability usage:
    a. Engine tests Cost validity (Ability class method?)
    b. Engine tests Target validity (Ability class method?)
    c. Engine retrieves Effects.
    d. For each Effect:
        I. Invoke Effect.actuate with reference to target. (parameters?)
